SOCCER - DUTCH REST RONALD DE BOER AGAINST SAN MARINO . The Netherlands will rest Dutch Player of the Year Ronald de Boer from Saturday ' s World Cup qualifier against San Marino in Amsterdam , Dutch ANP news agency said on Thursday . The attacking Ajax Amsterdam midfielder , who is carrying a niggling knee injury , will sit out what the Dutch expect to be a formality . However , in next Wednesday ' s key qualifier away in Turkey , he is set to replace Arsenal striker Dennis Bergkamp who will be allowed to miss that match because of his fear of flying . The Dutch top group seven with three wins from three games . 
